325
00:11:16,828 --> 00:11:17,571
Nothing at all.

326
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:18,273
Excellent.

327
00:11:18,293 --> 00:11:19,095
That's brilliant.

328
00:11:19,636 --> 00:11:20,018
Okay.

329
00:11:21,321 --> 00:11:24,529
