No, no, so it's a fairly standard new build at the moment.

335
00:11:38,748 --> 00:11:40,669
Okay, and you're happy with work?

336
00:11:41,549 --> 00:11:43,412
plenty of work at the moment, so that's good.

337
00:11:43,432 --> 00:11:44,873
Great, excellent.

338
00:11:44,893 --> 00:11:48,015
And what about, you said you've got a girlfriend, do you live with her?

339
00:11:48,036 --> 00:11:48,375
I do.

340
00:11:48,796 --> 00:11:49,777
Right, okay.

341
00:11:49,797 --> 00:11:52,298
And you're happy, everything's good at home?

342
00:11:52,639 --> 00:11:53,059
Yeah, it's fine.

343
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:53,860
No stresses?

344
00:11:54,540 --> 00:11:55,422
No, no.

345
00:11:55,442 --> 00:11:56,623
Excellent, okay.

346
00:11:56,602 --> 00:11:59,908
