Is it?

365
00:12:25,835 --> 00:12:26,134
Okay.

366
00:12:26,515 --> 00:12:29,040
And at what age did you start smoking?

367
00:12:29,922 --> 00:12:31,581
It would have been about 30.

368
00:12:32,326 --> 00:12:33,629
Age 30.

369
00:12:33,649 --> 00:12:34,029
Okay.

370
00:12:34,049 --> 00:12:35,453
Have you thought about giving up?

371
00:12:36,001 --> 00:12:38,005
Well, not really, not at the moment.

372
00:12:38,918 --> 00:12:41,081
