373
00:12:42,306 --> 00:12:42,482
No, no.

374
00:12:42,502 --> 00:12:43,063
Okay.

375
00:12:43,084 --> 00:12:46,008
Well, when you do, we're here any time.

376
00:12:46,048 --> 00:12:54,000
We've got lots of support strategies in place, so whenever you feel you would like to talk about stopping smoking, we're here just to let you know, okay?

377
00:12:54,561 --> 00:12:56,663
I just want to ask you about your alcohol intake.

378
